---
title: Tender Beef Rump & Peppercorn Sauce with Crushed Parmesan Baby Potatoes & Greens
description: There’s something eternally comforting about the aroma of a creamy peppercorn sauce. Completely mouth-watering to say the least. Drizzled over tender beef rump with a side of cheesy baby potatoes and aromatic veggies, it’s time for pub-style steak and
chips to move over; there’s a new contender in town.
